   Cao, Christian; Boucher, Emily; Donnici, Claire; Whelan, Mairead; Rahim, Hannah, Univ Calgary, Cumming Sch Med, Calgary, AB, Canada.
   Liu, Michael, Univ Oxford, Dept Social Policy \& Intervent, Oxford, England.
   Yanes-Lane, Mercedes, McGill Univ, COVID Immun Task Force 19, Montreal, PQ, Canada.
   Perlman-Arrow, Sara; Evans, Timothy Grant, McGill Univ, Sch Populat \& Global Hlth, Montreal, PQ, Canada.
   Chen, Judy, McGill Univ, Fac Med \& Hlth Sci, Montreal, PQ, Canada.
   Duarte, Nathan; Van Wyk, Jordan; Atmaja, Austin; Rocco, Simona; Joseph, Abel, Univ Waterloo, Fac Engn, Waterloo, ON, Canada.
