   Cruz, Marco A. S.; Oliveira, Ewerton L. S., HP Inc Brazil R\&D, BR-90619900 Porto Alegre, RS, Brazil.
   Winkler, Ingrid, SENAI CIMATEC Univ Ctr, Management \& Ind Technol Dept, BR-41650010 Salvador, BA, Brazil.
   Nascimento, Erick G. S., Univ Surrey, Surrey Inst People Centred AI, Fac Engn \& Phys Sci, Sch Comp Sci \& Elect Engn, Guildford GU2 7XH, England.},
DOI = {10.3390/bdcc7010015},
Article-Number = {15},
