   Nardone, Anthony; Valenciano, Marta, Epiconcept, Dept Epidemiol, Paris, France.
   Cheng, Brianna, McGill Univ, Sch Populat \& Global Hlth, Montreal, PQ, Canada.
   Noel, Kim; Yanes-Lane, Mercedes; Buckeridge, David, McGill Univ, Dept Epidemiol Biostat \& Occupat Hlth, Montreal, PQ, Canada.
   Yanes-Lane, Mercedes, McGill Univ, COVID 19 Immun Task Force Secreteriat, Montreal, PQ, Canada.
