   Khan, Hassan Aqeel; Kamboh, Awais Mehmood, Univ Jeddah, Engn Coll, Jeddah, Saudi Arabia.
   Butt, Hammad Tanveer; Stricker, Didier, Tech Univ Kaiserslautern, Dept Comp Sci, Kaiserslautern, Germany.
   Butt, Hammad Tanveer, Natl Univ Sci \& Technol NUST, Coll Elect \& Mech Engn, Islamabad, Pakistan.
   Shafait, Saima; Alamgir, Wasim, Pak Emirates Mil Hosp, Rawalpindi, Pakistan.
