   Shahpar, Mohsen Akbari; Asgari-Chenaghlu, Meysam, Univ Tabriz, Fac Elect \& Comp Engn, Dept Comp Engn, Tabriz 51368, Iran.
   Jaryani, Farhang, Arak Univ AU, Fac Engn, Arak 802111, Iran.
