   Edomwande, Maxwell, Nuance Commun Inc, Burlington, MA USA.
   Otokiti, Ahmed Umar, Digitial Hlth Solut LLC, 455 Tarrytown Rd Suite 1181, White Plains, NY 10607 USA.},
