   Granja, Raquel; Silva, Ana Maria; Goncalves, David, Univ Coimbra, Res Ctr Anthropol \& Hlth CIAS, Dept Life Sci, Calcada Martim de Freitas, P-3000456 Coimbra, Portugal.
   Granja, Raquel; Araujo, Ana Cristina; Silva, Ana Maria, Univ Lisbon, Fac Humanities, Ctr Archaeol, Univ Lisbon UNIARQ, Alameda Univ, P-1600214 Lisbon, Portugal.
   Lugli, Federico, Univ Modena \& Reggio Emilia, Dept Chem \& Geol Sci, Modena, Italy.
