   Liu, Tiebang; Rong, Han; Yang, Haichen, Shenzhen Kangning Hosp, Shenzhen Mental Hlth Ctr, Shenzhen, Peoples R China.
   Fang, Yiru, CAS Ctr Excellence Brain Sci \& Intelligence Techn, Shanghai, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.jad.2019.09.030},
Keywords = {Major depressive disorder; Health behavior; Symptoms; Machine learning;
