   Imam, Yahia, Hamad Med Corp HMC, Neurosci Inst, Neurol Sect, Doha, Qatar.
   Albalkhi, Ibrahem, Alfaisal Univ, Coll Med, Riyadh, Saudi Arabia.
   Albalkhi, Ibrahem, Great Ormond St Hosp NHS Fdn Trust, Dept Neuroradiol, Great Ormond St, London WC1N 3JH, England.
   Yaseen, Said, Jordan Univ Sci \& Technol, Sch Med, Irbid, Jordan.
