Affiliation = {Sheikhtaheri, A (Corresponding Author), Iran Univ Med Sci, Sch Hlth Management \& Informat Sci, Dept Hlth Informat Management, Tehran, Iran.
   Zarei, Javad; Jamshidnezhad, Amir; Hadianfard, Ali Mohammad, Ahvaz Jundishapur Univ Med Sci, Sch Allied Med Sci, Dept Hlth Informat Technol, Ahvaz, Iran.
