   Kim, Caron R.; Ganatra, Bela, WHO, Dept Sexual \& Reprod Hlth \& Res, Dev \& Res Training Human Reprod HRP, UNDP UNFPA UNICEF WHO World Bank Special Programm, Geneva, Switzerland.
   Feehan, Dennis; Breen, Casey, Univ Calif Berkeley, Berkeley, CA 94720 USA.},
DOI = {10.1186/s12978-022-01518-3},
