   SHOCKABLE RHYTHM; BLACK-BOX; SURVIVAL; RISK; TOOL; PROGNOSTICATION;
   APPLICABILITY; ALGORITHMS},
Author-Email = {fhajati@une.edu.au},
Number-of-Cited-References = {102},
